    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to the dish with your <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
